items.description: A generalizable machine learning-based performance modeling framework.

items.name: Handwritten-Character-Recognition-Project
items.description: I developed a machine learning model to recognize handwritten English alphabets (A-Z) from images. This project leverages the powerful combination of deep learning techniques and the MNIST dataset framework.

items.name: django_project
items.description: This is a simple example of deploying machine learning model using django framework

items.name: Hypernets
items.description: A General Automated Machine Learning framework to simplify the development of End-to-end AutoML toolkits in specific domains.

items.name: Crop-Care
items.description: Crop Care: A web application built with Python, Flask framework, and integrates machine learning models for precise disease diagnosis from uploaded leaf images.

items.name: AI-and-ML-Resources
items.description: Enhance your AI and ML journey with curated learning materials, libraries, frameworks, tools, and communities. Ideal for beginners and experienced developers seeking to level up their skills in artificial intelligence and machine learning.

items.name: TrialTranslator
items.description: Framework for in-silico reproduction of landmark oncology randomized controlled trials using machine learning survival models.

items.name: clustering-from-scratch
items.description: Machine learning clustering algorithm without any framework or library

items.name: options-pricing-ml
items.description: A comprehensive machine learning-based framework designed for predicting and analyzing option prices.

items.name: neuraC
items.description: A machine learning framework and visualisation tool, written in C.

items.name: cat-dog-classifier-flask
items.description: This project involves developing a web application using the Flask framework, which is then containerized and deployed using Docker. The application leverages a machine learning model from Hugging Face to classify. The Docker setup ensures that the application is portable.

items.name: Savvy_api
items.description: Savvy_api is an API project designed specifically to interface with Savvy-app, a mobile application developed using react native. This API is built using the Python FastAPI framework, ensuring  easy scalability to handle real-time financial transactions processing based on machine learning models using  banks SMS messages.

items.name: Random_Learning
items.description: Exploring some machine learning frameworks.
